                        <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-4">
                            Comprehensive guides, tutorials, and references for all Python versions. Start with the tutorial
                            and explore the standard library.
                        </p>
                        <a href="https://docs.python.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-primary">
                            Browse Docs →
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-python-yellow">
