                            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">IRC Chat</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-4">
                            Real-time chat with Python developers on Libera.Chat. Join #python for general help
                            or specialized channels for specific topics.
                        </p>
                        <a href="https://web.libera.chat/#python" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-primary">
                            Join IRC →
