                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Mailing Lists</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-4">
                            Subscribe to mailing lists for announcements, development discussions, and specialized topics.
                            Great for staying informed.
                        </p>
                        <a href="https://www.python.org/community/lists/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-primary">
                            View Lists →
